Measuring Impact
 
 






Products
TriLinc conducts extensive market research and designed its flagship fund, TriLinc Global Impact Fund, with the following characteristics:

Product theme with general market appeal
Impact opportunities that are measurable and reportable
Competitive, yield-oriented financial returns
Leveraged by experience of institutional quality managers with long-term track records
Capacity to scale to $1.5-2.0 billion














 


