What is Impact Investing?
Learn More









            TriLinc Global is a groundbreaking impact fund sponsor whose mission is to demonstrate the role that the capital markets can play in helping solve some of the world’s pressing economic, social and environmental challenges. TriLinc Global intends to set a high standard of transparency and accountability for delivering financial returns, and for tracking and reporting impact to investors. To bring about transformative change, we help investors recognize the power they have to set a new standard for capitalism by requiring companies to think differently about their role in society. Through intentionally selecting only those investments with potential to improve society while still generating competitive returns, TriLinc seeks to demonstrate that investors can do well by doing good. 















